<para>a in [0,1], a=0 =&gt; point is on next( e ) edge, a=1 =&gt; point is in dest( e ) b in [0,1], b=0 =&gt; point is on e edge, b=1 =&gt; point is in dest( next( e ) ) a+b in [0,1], a+b=0 =&gt; point is in org( e ), a+b=1 =&gt; point is on prev( e.sym() ) edge </para>
        </detaileddescription>
