    <briefdescription>
<para>encodes a point inside a triangular mesh face using barycentric coordinates </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Notations used below: <linebreak/>
 v0 - the value in org( e ) <linebreak/>
 v1 - the value in dest( e ) <linebreak/>
 v2 - the value in dest( next( e ) ) Generated from class <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1MeshTriPoint" kindref="compound">MR.MeshTriPoint</ref></computeroutput>. This is the non-const half of the class. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
